{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"@gintooooonic","author":"gintooooonic","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"304658b5-0241-5b3a-9efa-4dea4b2ef378","excerpt":"1. 영속성 컨텍스트 엔티티를 영구 저장하는 환경 EntityManager를 통해 접근  J2SE 환경에서는 EntityManager와 영속성 컨텍스트가 일대일 J2EE와 Spring 등 컨테이너 환경에서는 여러 개의 EntityManager가 하나의 영속성 컨텍스트와 연결 2. 엔티티의 생명 주기  비영속 (New) 영속성 컨텍스트와 전혀 관계가 없는 상태 엔티티를 갓 생성한 상태 영속 (Managed) 영속성 컨텍스트에 의해 관리되는 상태 DB…","html":"<h2 id=\"1-영속성-컨텍스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"1 영속성 컨텍스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 영속성 컨텍스트</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>엔티티를 영구 저장하는 환경</li>\n<li>\n<p>EntityManager를 통해 접근 <code class=\"language-text\">entityManager.persist(entity);</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>J2SE 환경에서는 EntityManager와 영속성 컨텍스트가 일대일</li>\n<li>J2EE와 Spring 등 컨테이너 환경에서는 여러 개의 EntityManager가 하나의 영속성 컨텍스트와 연결</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-엔티티의-생명-주기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%97%94%ED%8B%B0%ED%8B%B0%EC%9D%98-%EC%83%9D%EB%AA%85-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 엔티티의 생명 주기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 엔티티의 생명 주기</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 503px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"entity-lifecycle\"\n        title=\"entity-lifecycle\"\n        src=\"/static/74c211d58e6b1acdfeb59a2abfc89be0/a4078/entity-lifecycle.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/74c211d58e6b1acdfeb59a2abfc89be0/5a46d/entity-lifecycle.png 300w,\n/static/74c211d58e6b1acdfeb59a2abfc89be0/a4078/entity-lifecycle.png 503w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color: #888888; font-size: 12px;\">\n  https://ckck803.github.io/2021/02/16/JPA/persistence/\n</p>\n<h3 id=\"비영속-new\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B9%84%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-new\" aria-label=\"비영속 new permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>비영속 (New)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트와 전혀 관계가 없는 상태</li>\n<li>엔티티를 갓 생성한 상태</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">MyEntity</span> myEntity <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyEntity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyEntity<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"영속-managed\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-managed\" aria-label=\"영속 managed permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>영속 (Managed)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트에 의해 관리되는 상태</li>\n<li>DB에 저장되는 것을 의미하는 것이 아님, 영속성 컨텍스트가 저장하는 것</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">EntityManager</span> em <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> emf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createEntityManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// EntityManagerFactory emf;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">EntityTransaction</span> tx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> em<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getTransaction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 트랜잭션 시작</span>\n\nem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">persist</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myEntity<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// myEntity 영속 상태로 전환</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"준영속-detached\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A4%80%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-detached\" aria-label=\"준영속 detached permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>준영속 (Detached)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트에 저장되었다가 분리된 상태</li>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트는 이제 해당 엔티티를 알지 못하므로 변경 감지 등이 수행되지 않음</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// myEntity만 준영속 상태로 전환</span>\nem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myEntity<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 영속성 컨텍스트 초기화, 모든 엔티티가 준영속 상태로</span>\nem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 영속성 컨텍스트 종료, 모든 엔티티가 준영속 상태로</span>\nem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"삭제-removed\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AD%EC%A0%9C-removed\" aria-label=\"삭제 removed permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>삭제 (Removed)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>DB에 <code class=\"language-text\">delete</code> 쿼리를 날려 삭제된 상태</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">em<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">remove</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myEntity<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-영속성-컨텍스트의-기능\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EC%9D%98-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\" aria-label=\"3 영속성 컨텍스트의 기능 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 영속성 컨텍스트의 기능</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1차 캐시 : 같은 트랜잭션 안에서 한 번 가져왔던 엔티티를 캐싱</li>\n<li>동일성 보장 : 1차 캐시에 의해, 엔티티를 <code class=\"language-text\">==</code> 비교해도 <code class=\"language-text\">true</code></li>\n<li>트랜잭션을 지원하는 쓰기 지연 : 쓰기 쿼리를 모아놨다가 한번에 전송</li>\n<li>변경 감지 : 엔티티의 변경을 JPA가 자동으로 인식</li>\n<li>지연 로딩 : 엔티티를 실제 사용하는 시점에 가져옴</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-플러시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"4 플러시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 플러시</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트의 변경 사항을 DB에 동기화</li>\n<li>영속성 컨텍스트를 비우지 않으므로 1차 캐시 그대로</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">FlushModeType.AUTO</code> 모드에서 플러시가 발생하는 시점</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">em.flush();</code></li>\n<li>트랜잭션 커밋</li>\n<li>JPQL 쿼리 실행</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">FlushModeType.COMMIT</code> 모드에서 플러시가 발생하는 시점</p>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션 커밋</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/ORM-JPA-Basic\">김영한, 자바 ORM 표준 JPA 프로그래밍 - 기본편</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#1-%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\">1. 영속성 컨텍스트</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#2-%EC%97%94%ED%8B%B0%ED%8B%B0%EC%9D%98-%EC%83%9D%EB%AA%85-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\">2. 엔티티의 생명 주기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#%EB%B9%84%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-new\">비영속 (New)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-managed\">영속 (Managed)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#%EC%A4%80%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D-detached\">준영속 (Detached)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#%EC%82%AD%EC%A0%9C-removed\">삭제 (Removed)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#3-%EC%98%81%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EC%9D%98-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\">3. 영속성 컨텍스트의 기능</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#4-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EC%8B%9C\">4. 플러시</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"영속성 컨텍스트","date":"February 23, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/JPA/220223-persistence-context/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/JPA/220222-jpa-start/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JPA란"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/JPA/220223-entity-mapping/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"엔티티 매핑"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}